{"tid":308650,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"超hea廣島2日1夜","createTime":"2017-07-04T11:02:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-05T14:57:35.000Z","uid":41009,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"01512977ddd96e5d5bc210c8619107ca64853275","tid":308650,"uid":41009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T11:02:40.000Z","msg":"因為公司有日補假俾我揀幾時放都得<br />\n所以就整左個連假 2日1夜去廣島hea下<br />\n去既都係大路野<br />\n不過人地去5日 我去2日咁解<br />\n<br />\n搭夜行巴士 朝早5點就到廣島<br />\n就即刻出發去宮島<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/qmj23yrw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fqmj23yrw&h=21aa9773&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/dai4mr8c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdai4mr8c&h=cfc0c83f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n手機up相好煩<br />\n好多時都打側左張相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開左post先慢慢執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55d0ab3c219ec65ef3e479aa2f8311e4850e18b0","tid":308650,"uid":41009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T11:23:33.000Z","msg":"因為太早到<br />\n(搭左0705開果班船)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/75qawsui\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F75qawsui&h=5391245a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/i4z2up51\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fi4z2up51&h=8826cf3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鹿都未開工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/a94ejkyq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fa94ejkyq&h=70387488&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/czpnx5by\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fczpnx5by&h=978c55ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"123226e4c23456902c774ad160ae4eed9859c27a","tid":308650,"uid":7355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T11:30:04.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"4ebc4705499615d0cf7d5192aaca193e3ff666aa","tid":308650,"uid":41009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T11:33:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/4bjn2t1e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4bjn2t1e&h=8a9d3a3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/7fp3yevq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F7fp3yevq&h=56776692&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朝早去真係冇咩人 唔會阻住影相<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/h01vztfi\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fh01vztfi&h=ad8041e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/h25dmsa8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fh25dmsa8&h=b4ead0ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行左去張長櫈度坐低<br />\n點知坐坐下落雨 (今日日本打風)<br />\n開遮繼續坐<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/40ndrq23\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F40ndrq23&h=4650efe8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n到走果陣(9點左右) 開始見好多人入緊島<br />\n好彩黎得早<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/mk7vpisl\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fmk7vpisl&h=6adf4f5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/p5ch3s4k\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fp5ch3s4k&h=4e45b1f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9a9aef05394010fd541fa92cb9fd864481e9a89","tid":308650,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T11:36:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兩日一夜都去日本<br />\n唔會覺得機票錢唔抵咩"},{"pid":"d2266344e4888fc9bbea5d0d116ba48d2772c4c3","tid":308650,"uid":83172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T11:38:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兩日一夜都去日本<br />\n唔會覺得機票錢唔抵咩</blockquote><br />\n樓主應該本身係日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢搭夜行巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"468e7c255b9d13e7498e65a9dccca00c46072dff","tid":308650,"uid":41009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T11:39:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兩日一夜都去日本<br />\n唔會覺得機票錢唔抵咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我揸緊日本working visa<br />\n一有連假就成日周圍去 就快行勻成個西日本"},{"pid":"644678459328491e6b70e5266e0fa4feaf097dac","tid":308650,"uid":13504,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T11:42:13.000Z","msg":"哦,原來係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁無所謂,幾好,周圍去下"},{"pid":"e643b84321de29e4a062285b1cb678532bc512f2","tid":308650,"uid":42344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T11:45:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d2f8cafdbe436d519015afbd8ac5ee9e2e19ca","tid":308650,"uid":41009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T11:52:37.000Z","msg":"由離開宮島果陣就好L大雨<br />\n落到去洪水警報級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為太多時間 搭廣電慢慢過去原爆ドーム前 順便瞓下 落車都未夠11點<br />\n就入左間cafe食早餐 磨下時間再出發<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/aul67ocv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Faul67ocv&h=8889f916&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/kg3t0dho\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fkg3t0dho&h=7a8f5c39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n資料館係一入去就開始起雞皮<br />\n不過冇想像中咁恐怖<br />\n我d同事講過話佢係中學果陣去 睇完發惡夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0ighcev3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0ighcev3&h=bc19bb82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後去左食lunch<br />\n求其入左1間食定食 又hea下<br />\n呢排上網睇緊天龍八部小說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後就行去廣島城<br />\n終於停左雨 已經係下晏3點<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/qeziwt3k\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fqeziwt3k&h=e577a10c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/b4yvguc6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fb4yvguc6&h=b555a62d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行完個城其實隻腳好攰<br />\n所以諗左陣租唔租單車 108円/30min<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/mrgkyljt\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fmrgkyljt&h=1980de12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n結果都係搭巴士 去酒店checkin"},{"pid":"22f20bd93c063790457dfcd46a8bdd04066b3abe","tid":308650,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T11:54:15.000Z","msg":"好似幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鹿仔真係好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c69467bb5c632c2ee301bf5b2cf6cf41cea8c82","tid":308650,"uid":41009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T12:00:03.000Z","msg":"5點幾左右就去到酒店checkin<br />\n返房瞓左陣 7點半就出街食飯<br />\n求其去左酒店隔離間壽司舖食 又唔算貴<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/mvf7bpel\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fmvf7bpel&h=03a96ed7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實今日已經行晒我想行既地方<br />\n有d唔知聽日去邊好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為下晝2點巴士走人 所以唔想去咁遠<br />\n所以應該去二葉の里歴史の散歩道去睇神社就算"},{"pid":"551cffbdb85ced97911bd65a89112eee6e5e5674","tid":308650,"uid":80015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T12:13:16.000Z","msg":"睇完d相想再去多次廣島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上次去個大鳥居斷腳維修緊 , 睇唔到全貌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/bga39qme\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fbga39qme&h=1fe07957&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a4dc56cd1f2be5b4d647011f78c4e234068db84f","tid":308650,"uid":41009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T12:16:18.000Z","msg":"hea底都有負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食完飯買左甜品同咖啡返房嘆<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2lcasvz0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2lcasvz0&h=75262d34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本d便利店d咖啡真係好抵屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我飲開Iced Latte 大約180円左右1杯<br />\n除左7仔 其他都好飲<br />\n7仔個杯有晒糖同奶係入面 但我唔飲有糖既咖啡"},{"pid":"60e9d025ecbf20f1bf68353d9775d187aed64660","tid":308650,"uid":80015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T12:17:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/wrolze2h\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fwrolze2h&h=e08fce24&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0cee37de07be036b39d3a050419ee9361cfd0cbd","tid":308650,"uid":80015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T12:18:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>hea底都有負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食完飯買左甜品同咖啡返房嘆<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2lcasvz0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2lcasvz0&h=75262d34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本d便利店d咖啡真係好抵屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我飲開Iced Latte 大約180円左右1杯<br />\n除左7仔 其他都好飲<br />\n7仔個杯有晒糖同奶係入面 但我唔飲有糖既咖啡</blockquote><br />\nSORRY , 我禁錯制畀左負皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  原諒我<i