61","tid":308650,"uid":41009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T12:50:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好似幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鹿仔真係好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鹿仔真係好得意<br />\n不過<span style=\"color: red;\">奈良d鹿好惡</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未打晒就回左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"895ca8aa481dade0a51a5ecb862495cb568002f0","tid":308650,"uid":41009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T13:07:16.000Z","msg":"雖然冇人睇<br />\n不過都係補埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n琴晚阿媽打黎 問好唔好玩<br />\n佢聽到我講其實我想行既野已經行晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就話其實酒店都唔洗book 玩完就走得<br />\n<br />\n一早食完早餐 返房補左陣眠就checkout<br />\n好撚大雨 去到巴士站見到岩岩過左鐘數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好彩架車遲到<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/qpgonfle\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fqpgonfle&h=59d412a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去左行神社儲御朱印 不過冇行晒7間咁癲 <br />\n(落雨冇心情行同唔想用咁多錢)<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/8kwsj0n3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F8kwsj0n3&h=1675e522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行左1，3，4號就閃左<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/dq2x84th\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdq2x84th&h=84b55cf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n饒津神社<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1rbh2k9c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1rbh2k9c&h=4648185b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ba0vom67\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fba0vom67&h=0c7cb732&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鶴羽根神社<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vpiahecs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvpiahecs&h=bfc11680&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實廣島既建築全部都新起咁濟<br />\n因為原爆咩都炸平晒<br />\n冇炸爛既都會有牌寫明<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/hlj69fun\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fhlj69fun&h=565823fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廣島東照宮<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/e096rjmx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fe096rjmx&h=61174076&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過咁岩時間外 拎唔到御朱印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無緣就算<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/8jh54kdf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F8jh54kdf&h=c6fc4539&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就返左廣島站hea到2點搭巴士走<br />\n完"},{"pid":"61fef8e396730c43fe6fd9a9adf3efa5d1711f34","tid":308650,"uid":92185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T13:24:30.000Z","msg":"好奇一問樓主，你覺得係日本搵工易唔易？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f4a48a839eb17e91bda26b5d95ff6894a0bb229","tid":308650,"uid":41009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T13:46:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好奇一問樓主，你覺得係日本搵工易唔易？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得<br />\n只要你肯做 冇話搵唔到工<br />\n不過一開始搵工/轉工 對方會睇左你係咩visa先<br />\n<br />\n我岩岩4個月前先轉左工"}]}